2025-12-05IRCC, GAC, TBFinancial Administration ActCertain Fees in Respect of the Issuance of Identity and Travel Documents (2023 Türkiye and Syria Earthquakes) Remission OrderCertain Fees in Respect of the Issuance of Identity and Travel Documents (2023 Türkiye and Syria Earthquakes) Remission Order in order to remit fees associated with travel documents, citizenship certificates and consular services that were not collected for Canadians and permanent residents of Canada affected by the earthquakes occurring in Türkiye and Syria on February 6, 2023.N/A
subject: Certain Fees in Respect of the Issuance of Identity and Travel Documents (2023 Türkiye and Syria Earthquakes) Remission Order
precis: Certain Fees in Respect of the Issuance of Identity and Travel Documents (2023 Türkiye and Syria Earthquakes) Remission Order in order to remit fees associated with travel documents, citizenship certificates and consular services that were not collected for Canadians and permanent residents of Canada affected by the earthquakes occurring in Türkiye and Syria on February 6, 2023.
